e you would find when using two single doors next to each other.";i:63;s:128:"This is possibly the second most common size door though 1 ½ car and 2 ½ car garage doors are also starting to be more common.";i:64;s:21:"2 ½ Car Garage Door.";i:65;s:80:"Garage door standard sizes for 2 ½ car garage doors are slightly larger than a.";i:66;s:132:"Garage door windows come standard with double-strength glass for greater durability making them as functional as they are beautiful.";i:67;s:83:"Select from an array of decorative window styles to give your home a distinct look.";i:68;s:107:"Learn more about garage door window inserts and garage door windows kits from an Overhead Door distributor.";}}